(1)
West 153rd Street, west from, but not including Seventh, to and including Edgecombe Aves. The view shows the rear of billboards, which are on the east side of Macombs Place, from West 153rd to 152nd Streets.

August 29, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from a different angle, and including a portion of Harlem Lane Park, on the right.

August 29, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
